.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, woodworking
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, manager, freelancer, social-worker, pilot
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
2. the engineer is in an even position##4
3. the manager is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the manager##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the pilot##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the freelancer and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
7. the pilot is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess      | sudoku | rock-climbing | puzzles   | woodworking  |
| Job   | social-worker | pilot    | freelancer        | engineer | manager |

