.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, basketball, rowing, golf, biathlon
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, canadian, egyptian, japanese
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the egyptian##1
7. the brazilian is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Sport      | biathlon      | basketball | handball   | golf  | rowing  |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | australian | brazilian | japanese |

