.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, liverpool, marseilles, hamburg
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, engineer, paramedic, security-guard, software-developer
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
2. the engineer is between the software-developer and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the paramedic is the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the paramedic is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| City   | san-francisco        | hannover                | marseilles  | liverpool  | hamburg            |
| Job        | electrician | software-developer | engineer | paramedic | security-guard |

