2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
8. the paramedic is on the right of the electrician##1
9. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Sport   | swimming       | basketball   | snowboarding    | badminton    | weightlifting |
| Job        | firefighter | doctor | electrician | paramedic | librarian     |

