5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff, vegafina, fonseca, bolivar
1. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is the cain-smoker##1
6. the indian is between the egyptian and the chinese##2
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the indian##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | indian     | chinese | indonesian |
| Cigar           | davidoff | cain     | vegafina | bolivar    | fonseca      |

