3. the fan of jazz is the accountant##1
4. the fan of house is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
6. the lawyer is on the left of the dancer##1
7. the firefighter is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | lawyer | dancer | firefighter | accountant | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | classical | indie | disco    | jazz    | house  |

