The people use 5 different means of transport: van, car, skateboard, bus, ship
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the car##2
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the ship is the person eating pepper##1
6. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | garlic    | spinach  | broccoli      | radish     | pepper |
| Transport   | van | car | bus | skateboard | ship |

