.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, old-henry, montecristo, alhambra, prince
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, dancing, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is chess and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | prince   | alhambra  | old-henry     | davidoff | montecristo |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | traveling | chess      |

