.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus, eggplant, plum, tomato
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, bus, scooter, taxi, tram
1. the person eating plum is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating tomato is between the person eating asparagus and the person driving the airplane##2
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Food   | raspberry | plum | eggplant     | tomato     | asparagus |
| Transport     | taxi   | bus   | airplane | scooter | tram  |

