.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, card-games, cooking, photography, reading
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, adventure, satire, superhero, horror
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching satire movies is the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person watching horror movies##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person watching horror movies##2
7. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | photography | cooking | card-games | reading | baking     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero    | adventure   | horror       | satire | western |

