.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, punk, rock, soul
City: paris, prague, boston, new-york, liverpool
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to new-york##2
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan of disco##1
7. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | punk      | rock | soul     | indie      |
| City     | liverpool | prague | new-york | paris | boston |

 